column2: I suggest Christmas markets be off limits to cars . Close all streets to vehicles and just let people walk.
THIS IS THE NEW GERMANY ... ALLAH ACHBAR

He is not a 'suspect'.
He is from Saudi Arabia and he deliberately drove his car through the crowd in the Magdebourg Xmass  market in Eastern Germany.
OK.?
There are NO lone wolves ! None . Operating alone at the time does not make this evil a lone wolf.
What do you expect from mo slim
What about “ First, do no harm”?
Violence is a daily occurrence in US.
Most of them are.  Normal person would not make this type of blanket statement.
